XRP Non-Stop Strategy (TP 25% / SL 15%) is a continuous long-side trading system designed specifically for XRP. The strategy uses an EMA-based trend filter (EMA20/EMA50) to confirm bullish conditions before entering a long position. Each trade applies a fixed +25% Take Profit target and a −15% Stop Loss, calculated dynamically from the entry price.
When a trade closes—whether by TP or SL—the strategy automatically re-enters on the next qualifying signal, enabling uninterrupted position cycling.
Features include:
• EMA-based trend confirmation
• Dynamic TP/SL visualization on the chart
• Clear BUY and EXIT markers
• Dedicated alert conditions for automation
